## ğŸ¯ Use Cases

SilanTui is perfect for:

- **System Administration Tools** - Server management, monitoring dashboards
- **Development Tools** - Build tools, deployment scripts, code generators
- **Data Processing** - ETL pipelines, data analysis tools
- **Interactive Applications** - Games, tutorials, wizards
- **AI Applications** - Chatbots, code assistants, content generators (optional)

## ğŸ—ï¸ Architecture

```
SilanTui Framework
â”œâ”€â”€ Core UI Components
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ ModernLogger      # Logging & output
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ UIBuilder         # Component builder
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ ChatDisplay       # Chat interface
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ LiveDisplay       # Real-time updates
â”‚
â”œâ”€â”€ Command System
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ CommandRegistry   # Command management
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ CommandBuilder    # Fluent command API
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ CommandManager    # Alias management
â”‚
â”œâ”€â”€ Optional Features
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ AI Client         # Universal AI integration
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ SessionManager    # State persistence
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ ThemeSystem       # Color customization
â”‚
â””â”€â”€ Examples
    â”œâ”€â”€ Dashboard         # Data visualization
    â”œâ”€â”€ Task Manager      # CRUD application
    â””â”€â”€ AI Chat           # Optional AI app
```

